"766","Additional Information About Minimum Required Investment"
"767","Shareholders can open a fund account with as little as $500 and"
"768","make subsequent investments in any amount. The minimum"
"769","investment is waived if you make regular investments weekly,"
"770","semi monthly, or monthly through automatic deductions through"
"771","your bank checking or savings account. Currently, Putnam is"
"772","waiving the minimum, but reserves the right to reject initial"
"773","investments under the minimum."
